<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣١٢٧ - ض ع ض ع]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ضعضعَ يضعضع، ضعضعةً، فهو مُضعضِع، والمفعول مُضعضَع<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• ضعضع البناءَ:</span> دكَّه، هدمه حتَّى الأرض <span class="c1">"ضعضع خُطَّة خَصْمِه: أفسدها"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• ضعضع الرَّجلَ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١ - أضعفَه <span class="c1">"ضعضعته النوائِبُ"</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٢ - أخضعه وأذلّه.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>